EmailTemplate.description: To Partner Applicants - For Credit Check
EmailTemplate.name: Partner Application - Credit Email
EmailTemplate.subject: Credit Check Request
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Lead.Name},
Adequate credit capacity is a critical characteristic of a successful SunPower dealer partner. With this in mind, we require prospective dealer partners to apply for credit prior to executing the SunPower dealer agreement. The credit application process is brief, just follow these steps:
1. Complete the attached credit application for SunPower Dealer Partners. Please complete this document thoroughly; missing information will result in a delayed decision. 2. Provide a copy of your companys financials, i.e. the most recent full year financials, e.g. 2013, with a balance sheet and concurrent income statement. 3. Please return these two items as attachments to credit@sunpowercorp.com or fax # 408-608-2034. When you return these items to the above mentioned email address, do NOT copy any other SunPower email addresses or anyone else. For privacy reasons you should only forward these items to the credit address (credit@sunpowercorp.com ). 4. Please specify in your email to Credit the amount of credit you are requesting. 5. Please include all contact information for the person who the credit team can contact with any questions.
Please keep in mind that incomplete information within items 1 and 2 above will lead to delays and possibly a lower credit limit; this is a critical issue since we see credit capacity as a primary consideration when we evaluate a market and a dealer partners ability to grow and achieve market share.
Thank you very much
Regards, (CSR NAME) SunPower Customer Service 1800 - SUNPOWER dealerapplicants@sunpower.com
